quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  99,1,"When the earth is shaken violently in its [last] quaking"
  99,2,when the earth throws out its burdens
  99,3,"when man cries, ‘What is happening to it?’"
  99,4,"on that Day, it will tell all"
  99,5,"because your Lord will inspire it [to do so]"
  99,6,"On that Day, people will come forward in separate groups to be shown their deeds"
  99,7,whoever has done an atom’s-weight of good will see it
  99,8,but whoever has done an atom’s-weight of evil will see that